</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_263" id="131r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_263_r1l20">Lantgraf Johanſen cʒum <expan>leutemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_263_r1l21">vnd Grafen cʒu Halls </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_263_r1l22">Gnedıger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Vns hat 
<del rend="strikethrough">dankler Pirker vnſ </del> Dankwart pirker <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_263_r1l23"> <expan>
<add>furg<ex>elegt</ex></add></expan> vvie 
<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ </del> Jm ewr gnade gen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> vettern lantgraf <expan>Leupold<ex>en</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> gar </del> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_263_r1l24">der venknüſʒ vvegen als Jn derſelb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> vetter gefangen hat / gar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_263_r1l25"> <expan>fürderlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gevveſen ſeẏ 
<del rend="strikethrough">t </del> / des vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_263_line_1576579795776_2360">vnd <expan>bıte<ex>n</ex></expan> etc daʒ Jr dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnedige hılff vnd <expan>fürdr<ex>ung</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_263_r1l28">gen dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>vett<ex>er</ex>n</expan> fürbaʒ <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_263_line_1576579798860_2365"><expan>gnedıkl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_263_r1l29">
<del rend="strikethrough">ob </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_263_line_1587140895966_759">daʒ </ab></add> Er der venknüſʒe ledig werde / Als etc das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_263" id="131r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Lantgraf Johansen czum <expan>Leutemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> und grafen czu
                        Halls </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat Dankwart Pirker,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                        <expan><add>furg<ex>elegt</ex></add></expan>, wie im ewr gnade gen
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> vettern lantgraf
                                <expan>Leupold<ex>en</ex></expan> von der venknüsz wegen, als in
                        derselb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> vetter gefangen hat, gar
                                <expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gewesen sey, des wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz
                                <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc., daz ir dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnedige
                        hilff und <expan>fürdr<ex>ung</ex></expan> gen dem
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>vett<ex>er</ex>n</expan> fürbaz <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><expan>gnedikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan></add>
<expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, <add>daz</add> er der venknüsze
                        ledig werde. Als etc. Das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
